that contained 1/3 the amount of posts as the most posted (Us of course) received the most attention in fixes.  His reply was that most the people that post in those(wizard) forums are confused, and are voicing things that have to do with class equality than class problems...In other words, we are upset because we don't do as much damage as warriors etc..etc..OK..Hmm isnt that verants vision, make all equally weighted ?  And what about the origional vision of Wizards &quot;being the masters of damage&quot; ?  So, my friends, it is sad for me to report from the horses mouth...don't expect alot of empathy from verant.  I asked about our inherent ineptness against Magic resisting uber HP velious Mobs..and he more or less just shrugged.. I then stated that I guess, unless you endure the trails of being a wizard 1ST HAND, you couldnt possibly empathize with our plight.  He admitted he had never played a wizard, so basically could not relate.  What a reassuring feeling to be destined to the fate determined by people who have no frame of referance or perspective that have the mentality of &quot;you teleport my uber Rogue just fine..what is your problem ?&quot;  Anyway..if they don't fix us, I for one will be joining the crusade for a wizardless Norath..after all, Verants right..what the hell do we know anyway about playing our class..and where the hell did we get off thinking we could dish out damage as warriors do.  The great thing about this is it came after 9 hours of waiting on a petition response..that never came until I repetitioned.  I lost 4 FULL packs of gear, when I swapped packs with a friend to get runes..traded back..all packs (25Kpp stuff) gone.  I was told &quot;Kriggan, the server GM who controls this is on Sat-Wed 4pm-12 am, handles these issues.  Well the bastard got my petition at 4pm Monday, and was in his que until 12 am  when he proceeded to CLEAR his que, and go home..causing me to re-petition and get a response within seconds..from a guy who could do nothing for me..sound familiar ?  Verant hopes we will just shut up, and go away...we need to send a message that this kind of apathetic responses are unacceptable.  I personally had filed with the BBB in regards to Verants BS, and yes Kriggan was a key player in the suit..and this is what I get in return for his chastisment..but you know what ?  Verant's attorneys kissed my butt, and got me ALL my gear back that he had caused me to lose (long story, erroneous banning, corpse rotted nightmare). Until I brought it to that level though.. I was told, &quot;Is game policy, there is nothing we can do...&quot; DO NOT ACCEPT THIS BS from them. So if you have a legit complaint, the BBB page has your recourse..make them be accountable and professional. Verant's Customer Service Manager Thom is very affable (and no, youll never reach him on the phone).  Anyway, I thought I would pass this on..Good luck to you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvulp.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vulp</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/28/01 7:39 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant told me &quot;don't get your hopes up&quot;</span><hr size=1> Server Gm's aren't the ones that decide these issues, had you talked to a member of the dev team i would be more worried <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucanadina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Canadina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 44<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/3/01 6:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant told me &quot;don't get your hopes up&quot;</span><hr size=1> Aye yes..lol<br>
